msgid ""
"💡 This process can be <strong>automated</strong> by setting an 'Email "
"Template' on the 'Planned' stage of your project (or any other stage you'd "
"like). A pre-made email template is available to you."
msgstr ""
"💡 Tämän prosessin voi <strong>automatisoida</strong> asettamalla "
"'sähköpostipohjan' projektisi 'suunniteltu'-tilaan (tai mihin tahansa "
"haluamaasi tilaan). Ennalta tehty sähköpostipohja on saatavilla."

